fans were on display throughout the building, and the upstairs
corridor featured mementos from Brown's career.
</P>
<P>
   Augusta-Richmond County Fire Chief Ronnie Few said the extent of
the damage had not been determined.
</P>
<P>
   Brown, 66, left for Myrtle Beach, S.C., on Thursday for two
concerts.
</P>
