decision to leave him shot and killed her and two others and then killed
himself, authorities said. Raeann Rice, who told family members that her
husband, Michael Rice, had pulled a gun on her several days earlier, returned to
her home about 1:30 p.m. today with her sister and her sister's boyfriend. About
6:15 p.m., members of a special weapons and tactics team looked in a back window
and saw the bodies of Rice and his wife at the bottom of the stairs.
